{"id":4204,"date":"2024-12-16T14:47:56","date_gmt":"2024-12-16T14:47:56","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=4204"},"modified":"2024-12-16T14:49:14","modified_gmt":"2024-12-16T14:49:14","slug":"relic-maniac","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/misc-info\/useful-npcs\/relic-maniac\/","title":{"rendered":"Relic Maniac (NPC)"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table grey left\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Location<\/th>\n<td><strong>Gurun Town<\/strong> &#8211; Inside of the house directly behind the Gurun Town Pok\u00e9mon Center.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Purpose<\/th>\n<td>Purchases all relics from the player.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Transaction Item<\/th>\n<td>Poke Dollars<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Cost<\/th>\n<td>N\/A<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h2>Location<\/h2>\n<p>Fly to the Gurun Town Pokemon Center and follow the brown path going north.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/12\/01-pokemon-unbound-standing-outside-of-the-gurun-town-pokemon-center.jpg\" alt=\"Standing outside of the Gurun Town Pokemon Center. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Standing outside of the Gurun Town Pokemon Center.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Enter the house northwest of the Regi Statue.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/12\/02-pokemon-unbound-entering-the-house-northeast-of-the-pokemon-center.jpg\" alt=\"Entering the house northeast of the Pokemon Center. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Entering the house northeast of the Pokemon Center.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The Relic Maniac is the Black Belt NPC inside of the house.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/12\/03-pokemon-unbound-approaching-the-relic-maniac.jpg\" alt=\"Approaching the Relic Maniac. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Approaching the Relic Maniac.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2>Purpose<\/h2>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/12\/04-pokemon-unbound-the-relic-maniac-asking-for-relics.jpg\" alt=\"The Relic Maniac asking for relics. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The Relic Maniac asking for relics.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The Relic Maniac purchases relics from you for a hefty price. You\u2019ll obtain these Relic items during the <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/mission-079\/\">Treasure Hunter mission<\/a> in the Tomb of Borrius.<\/p>\n<p>Below is a list of most relics the Relic Maniac purchases (what we\u2019ve been able to test), along with the amount of Poke Dollars you can expect for selling them.<\/p>\n<table class=\"table grey center zebra even-2col\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Relic<\/th>\n<th>Price<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Relic Silver<\/td>\n<td>5,000 Poke Dollars<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Relic Band<\/td>\n<td>100,000 Poke Dollars<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Relic Gold<\/td>\n<td>10,000 Poke Dollars<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Relic Crown<\/td>\n<td>300,000 Poke Dollars<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Relic Statue<\/td>\n<td>200,000 Poke Dollars<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/misc-info\/useful-npcs\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"299\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/useful-npc-preview.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/useful-npc-preview.jpg 300w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/useful-npc-preview-200x200.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-inf